Package com.gliwka.hyperscan.wrapper

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    Database containing compiled expressions ready for scanning using the Scanner
    Expression
    Expression to be compiled as a Database and then be used for scanning using the Scanner
    Match
    Represents a match found during the scan
    Scanner
    Scanner, can be used with databases to scan for expressions in input string In case of multithreaded scanning, you need one scanner instance per thread.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ExpressionFlag
    Flags influencing the matching behaviour of the scanner for a particular Expression
  • Exception Summary
